{"tid":1603040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黑警可能又打死人呀","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:06:45.000Z","uid":232062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d72ea103d8b1147ca8eef17b0feb9440f5b2908e","tid":1603040,"uid":232062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:58:01.000Z","msg":"金鐘灣仔銅鑼灣站有設施遭破壞 或未能明天恢復服務<br />\n2019-09-29 HKT 22:50<br />\n 分享工具 facebook twitter<br />\n港鐵表示，港島區發生大型公眾活動期間，多個港鐵車站，包括金鐘站、灣仔站及銅鑼灣站均有車站設施遭受破壞。工程人員稍後會檢查及盡力復修，但部分車站或設施，有機會未能在明天恢復提供服務，呼籲乘客留意公布。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，今日有人非法使用車內緊急出口及軌道的斜道，更有示威者投擲汽油彈進入車站及在車站出入口縱火，嚴重威脅公眾及港鐵員工的安全，港鐵予以最強烈譴責，強調絕不容忍任何危害鐵路安全的行為，公司已報警處理。<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">手足試過好多次破壞黨鐵設施，但除左831大家都知道打死左人之外，根本冇試過封站多過一日，今次又封站，係咪又有831事件重演??</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9c552277e5a32081c1015f55376fad8f8e935bd","tid":1603040,"uid":104811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},{"pid":"5b164e4a1262ab20d0f603c7315c01798f9cb030","tid":1603040,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a87eab7ad85323c6be1290ef5babcbc1591e2f","tid":1603040,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"[twitter懶人包]全部同我入泥！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602587</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n#法律知識<br />\n<br />\n警方可以根據警隊條例54(1)對任何行動可疑的人，或54(2)對任何有合理懷疑已犯法的人進行截查。<br />\n<br />\n若你被無理截查，本頻道建議直接引用法律條文質問警方：<br />\n✅根據哪一條警隊條例進行截查；<br />\n✅如果回答54(1)，可追問警方為何你行動可疑；<br />\n✅如果回答54(2)，請追問警方為何懷疑你已經或準備犯法。<br />\n<br />\n案例指出警方應根據客觀事實（時間、地點、現場情況、行為等）作主觀判斷。<br />\n<br />\n‼️截查期間，警方不能要求你解鎖或關閉手機。"},{"pid":"37ef2efe425465d168ebde71d277f034905e6c0b","tid":1603040,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"睇清楚啲先"},{"pid":"0679884505239ab0a9f848236837624a515d6f8a","tid":1603040,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"收皮啦黨鐵"},{"pid":"2000e9fe2e93b5cd75ffceabccd250529cd391dc","tid":1603040,"uid":312412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:02:16.000Z","msg":"[twitter懶人包]全部同我入泥！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602587</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"22fcc7cfe9cde5f3e94425d85f53f65479412ee5","tid":1603040,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9c552277e5a32081c1015f55376fad8f8e935bd","tid":1603040,"uid":104811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"熱門完全唔見有，可唔可以幫手推post"},{"pid":"ce262970be564794dc91028c17e2ad8dc8e06f63","tid":1603040,"uid":213597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:03:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66867dfd71f31aaf601bfe3b52f348d71cb4ae30","tid":1603040,"uid":46078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:03:55.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},{"pid":"82271ce0119c223fa84f6d9bf88896a380acf89e","tid":1603040,"uid":104811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22fcc7cfe9cde5f3e94425d85f53f65479412ee5","tid":1603040,"uid":289694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9c552277e5a32081c1015f55376fad8f8e935bd","tid":1603040,"uid":104811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:58:21.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"熱門完全唔見有，可唔可以幫手推post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1